    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 13. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) abludens sp. nov., sperm induction structures, female, variant forms. 10 ‒ 11. Normal forms; 12 ‒ 13. Aberrant forms in strongly pressed specimens. Not scaled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/322029/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.322032>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 26. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) bergomensis sp. nov., sperm induction structures, female, variant forms. Not scaled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/322032/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.322038>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49 – 52. Sperm induction structures, females, variant forms. 49 ‒ 50. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) marcovallei sp. nov. (49. Normal form; 50. Aberrant form in strongly pressed specimen); 51 ‒ 52. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) pantinii sp. nov. (51. Normal form; 52. Aberrant form in strongly pressed specimen). Not scaled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/322038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.322040>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57 – 62. Sperm induction structures, females. 57. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) longisetis; 58. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) brevipilis; 59. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) longulus; 60. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) distinctus; 61. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) vicarius; 62. Pachylaelaps (Longipachylaelaps) carpathicus. Not scaled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/322040/files/figure.png" ;
